skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: porsche club
des: The Connecticut Valley Region of the Porsche Club of America has quite a lot of activities throughout the year for members to enjoy driving their Porsches and socialize with each other. You can use this skill to find out what and when are upcoming events on the calendar. Then all you have to do is count the days until the time comes when you and other enthusiastic club members get together to have fun.
